snippet.title: Party Planet Debut Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Party Planet is a fun-packed compilation of 30 games, and it's available now on Nintendo Switch™!
Visit https://mastiff.games/partyplanet-site for more information.

Anyone, regardless of age or skill level, will have an absolute blast playing any of the 30 party games, 18 of which can be played with up to 4 players for some friendly cooperative or competitive play.
